snippet.title: Pro Cycling Manager 2020 | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy Pro Cycling Manager 2020: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1178400/Pro_Cycling_Manager_2020/

Step in the shoes of a Team Manager of the Grand Boucle. Manage your cyclists' training, schedule races, keep morale high or sign contracts with new sponsors! Everything is easier with the updated Dashboard for a better visibility and your assistant manager!

#ProCylingManager2020 is now available on Steam.
